if_this_is_a_true_value ? then_the_result_is_this : else_it_is_this

                URL                 Helper                      Description
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
member          /photos/1/preview   preview_photo_path(photo)   Acts on a specific resource so required id (preview specific photo)
